OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian oil getting into UK
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fvia refinery loophole      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Millions of barrels of fuel made from  
OL,6, Russian oil are still being imported to
OL,7, the UK despite sanctions imposed over  
OL,8, the war in Ukraine, research claims.   
OL,10,FA so-called "loophole" means Russian   
OL,11,Fcrude is refined in countries such as  
OL,12,FIndia and the products sold to the UK. 
OL,14,FThis is not illegal and does not breach
OL,15,Fthe UK's Russian oil ban, but critics  
OL,16,Fsay it undermines sanctions aimed at   
OL,17,Frestricting Russia's war funds.        
OL,19,FThe UK government denied there had been
OL,20,Fany imports of Russian oil since 2022. 
